"{\"uid\": \"abc.net.au-news-2024-06-15-tributes-flow-for-cate-campbell-as-olympic-dream-ends-103983326\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Personalise the news and  stay in the know  Emergency  Backstory  Newsletters  \\u4e2d\\u6587\\u65b0\\u95fb  BERITA BAHASA INDONESIA  TOK PISIN  Find any issues using dark mode?Please let us know  Sport  Topic:Swimming  Campbell was overwhelmed with support from her teammates and competitors after her final race.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BAHASA INDONESIA\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Chris Hyde)  There was not a dry eye in the house.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"score\": 0.9999752325781989, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hyde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A capacity crowd at the Brisbane Aquatic Centre saw the end of an era as Cate Campbell bowed out after a stunning career.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9998887160797877, \"rank\": 7.387510546337463e-05, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ending may have been one of disappointment - heartbreak, even - as Campbell failed in her ambitious bid to reach a fifth Olympic Games, 16 years after she burst onto the scene in Beijing as a 16-year-old.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998894964, \"rank\": 1.1068989473675447e-10, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had hoped for the fairytale ending, and it's what I had worked for and what I felt I was capable of,\\\" a tearful Campbell said.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And unfortunately, my body just said no.\\\"\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell's home crowd gave her a rousing ovation before and after the race.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Chris Hyde)  Campbell endured the traumatic experience offailing to qualify for the 100 metres final on Friday, leaving the pool with her dreams of competing at the Paris Games hanging by a thread.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"score\": 0.9999752325781989, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hyde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\"}, {\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one of the highest-quality 100m freestyle fields in Australian swimming history, four-time Olympic gold medallist Cate Campbell misses out on making the final by just 0.01 seconds.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cate Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That thread was tugged byqualifying for the 50 metres freestyle on Saturday morning.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But sadly, it was not to be, as Campbell finished in seventh spot.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the end, and it's a perfect way to exit the pool,\\\" Campbell said through tears.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My first major competition was in this swimming pool, maybe over 20 years ago \\u2026 I warmed up in this pool just behind us for the first time as a nine-year-old.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And tonight I warmed up in it as a 32-year-old.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got to walk out and swim in a swimming pool that I have competed in so many times, that I have qualified for teams in, that I have broken world records in.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I looked up at the stand at the spot where my dad used to buy every newspaper under the sun because he had a swimming carnival to sit through for two days.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This place and this sport has embedded itself so deeply into me that I just feel really, really privileged that, if it was going to end, it was going to end this way in front of this crowd and the people who I love.\\\"\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cate Campbell had been battling illness throughout Trials week.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cate Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Chris Hyde)  Campbell ends her career as one of the greatest Australian swimmers of all time.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2409, \"end\": 2419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"score\": 0.9999752325781989, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hyde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\"}, {\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999964085105523, \"rank\": 3.591404654028544e-06, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 32-year-old has won 37 major international medals - 23 of them gold.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fierce competitor that always bought her best to relay swims, Campbell has excelled as a mentor and role model for countless swimmers.\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was evident in the way her competitors crowded her in the pool at the conclusion of the race.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In scenes that will linger long in the memory of everyone who saw them, each woman paid homage to the doyen of Australian women's sprinting one last time, with tears flowing freely.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, Cate has really set up this for a lot of us women,\\\" Mollie Callaghan said.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cate and sister Bronte embrace after the 50m final.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3102, \"end\": 3108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.052111875365938e-41, \"text\": \"Bronte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Quinn Rooney)  \\\"She set the standards, and she's one of the most inspirational women, in and out of the water.\\\"\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Emma McKeon said it was an \\\"emotional moment\\\" when everyone crowded around her.\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3265, \"end\": 3276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just sharing that with Cate and, like, she's inspired all of us,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's been at the top of the sprint freestyle game for like, I do not even know how long, like longer than I have been swimming, probably.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell herself could not believe the reaction of her competitors.\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3565, \"end\": 3573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not [begrudge] anyone for only looking at results, but the fact that there were two girls who qualified for an Olympic Games - which is no mean feat, one of them for her first individual squad, Meg Harris - that they put their celebrations on hold and and came over, it was one of the most incredible moments and something that I will cherish for the rest of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 4011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3837, \"end\": 3847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meg Harris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell looked up at the stands and waved as she walked out onto the pool deck.\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4013, \"end\": 4021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After she finished her TV commitments, she waved again, blowing kisses to the crowd.\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started in this sport because I was a a little girl who loved swimming,\\\" Campbell said, looking up at the stands with tears glistening in her eyes.\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4257, \"end\": 4265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.101925223021328e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did, I loved it more than anything else.\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ABC Sport Daily is your daily sports conversation.\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4378, \"end\": 4387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\", \"score\": 0.9999996973065667, \"rank\": 3.0269368804549345e-07, \"text\": \"ABC Sport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We dive into the biggest story of the day and get you up to speed with everything else that's making headlines.\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And over the years, that love has been tried and tested, and that relationship has been pushed to its absolute limits and its breaking point.\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I walked out tonight and I remembered that little girl who walked out behind those blocks for the first time, and I remembered the joy and the love that I have for the sport.\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was able to do that in front of my friends and my family and my loved ones.\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest hug was reserved, of course, for little sister Bronte.\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 5013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5006, \"end\": 5012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.052111875365938e-41, \"text\": \"Bronte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair, who trained together for so long but completed this, their final Olympics qualification campaign, apart, will end their careers at different times too.\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Cate believes there is a symmetry in that too.\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, she watched me at my first Olympics from the couch, and I will get to do the same for her last Olympics,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a story idea about women in sport?\", \"from\": 5358, \"to\": 5404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Email usabcsport5050@your.abc.net.au  LIVE  LIVE  Topic:Golf  Topic:Golf  Analysis by Dean Bilton  Topic:Heatwaves  Topic:World Politics  Analysis by David Taylor  Topic:World Politics  Topic:US Elections  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Brisbane  Olympic Games  Sport  Swimming  Topic:Heatwaves  Topic:World Politics  Analysis by David Taylor  Topic:World Politics  Topic:US Elections  Topic:Wildlife Traffic Accidents and Incidents  Topic:Golf  LIVE  Topic:Arson  We acknowledge Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples as the First Australians and Traditional Custodians of the lands where we live, learn, and work.\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 6109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5492, \"end\": 5496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.434752097466793e-17, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 5497, \"end\": 5503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilton-in-Ainsty\", \"score\": 0.9993578613394078, \"rank\": 0.0003218441671708253, \"text\": \"Bilton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilton-in-Ainsty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilton-in-Ainsty\"}, {\"begin\": 5967, \"end\": 5977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"score\": 0.9455529241908074, \"rank\": 0.05758214741576423, \"text\": \"Aboriginal\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 6054, \"end\": 6064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hands_of_the_Cause\", \"score\": 0.5558378367567778, \"rank\": 0.7990858733810513, \"text\": \"Custodians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hands_of_the_Cause\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hands_of_the_Cause\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This service may include material from Agence France-Presse (AFP), APTN, Reuters, AAP, CNN and the BBC World Service which is copyright and cannot be reproduced.\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6150, \"end\": 6170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agence France-Presse\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 6178, \"end\": 6182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aboriginal_Peoples_Television_Network\", \"score\": 0.9949371207158572, \"rank\": 0.005088642466255633, \"text\": \"APTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aboriginal_Peoples_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aboriginal_Peoples_Television_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 6184, \"end\": 6191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9474512896981979e-19, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 6198, \"end\": 6201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.599389030495148e-13, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 6210, \"end\": 6227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_World_Service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.768010368614233e-16, \"text\": \"BBC World Service\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_World_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_World_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AEST= Australian Eastern Standard Time which is 10 hours ahead of GMT (Greenwich Mean Time)\", \"from\": 6274, \"to\": 6365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6274, \"end\": 6278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 6291, \"end\": 6